      "english_name": "Witness chronicle — recognition + seal pairs",
      "description": "Every memory attestation atomically emits a recognition chronicle entry on subject's timeline AND a seal chronicle entry on witness's timeline. State: list of (recognition, seal) pairs, each parent_chronicle_id-linked. Order: prefix order. Iteration: pairs ↦ pairs ++ [(new_recognition, new_seal)]. Cap: architectural-unbounded. Witness: chronicle entries on both timelines; parent_chronicle_id chains the DAG.",
